Class ApplicationCreateRequest

java.lang.Object
com.atu.green_global_initiative_api.model.dao.request.ApplicationCreateRequest
public class ApplicationCreateRequest extends Object
Request DTO for creating a new application in the Green Global Initiative API. This class contains the necessary information required to create a new application.
